<h2 id="exercise">Exercise</h2>

<p>给 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">MoreStlc.v</code> 里的 StlcE 写 typechecker, 然后 prove soundness / completeness （过程中用了非常 mega 的 tactics）</p>

<div class="language-coq highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c">(** 还不能这么写 **)</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="o">|</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="no">fst</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="no">p</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=&gt;</span><span class="w">
